  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    junit.framework.Test

    public class StorageManagerTest
extends com.google.gwt.junit.client.GWTTestCase
    GWT jUnit tests for the class StorageManager. In this test class, saving and retrieving of an initial distribution, a mixing protocol and a mixing result are tested.
    Author:
    Group Fingerpaint
